Verify Node.js Version: Ensure you have Node.js version >= 18.0.0 installed.

(Command: node -v)

Verify npm Version: Ensure you have npm version >= 9.0.0 installed.

(Command: npm -v)

Install Firebase CLI Globally: Install the Firebase CLI globally using npm.

(Command: npm install -g firebase-tools)

Verify Firebase CLI Version: Ensure Firebase CLI version >= 12.0.0 is installed.

(Command: firebase --version)

Clone Git Repository: Clone your ReelMeals repository from GitHub to your local machine.

(Command: git clone <repository_url>)

Navigate to Project Directory: Change your current directory to the cloned ReelMeals project folder.

(Command: cd drjdavid-reelmeals)

Install Project Dependencies: Install all project dependencies using npm.

(Command: npm install)

